  "title": "AN ACT AUTHORIZING THE CITY OF PROVIDENCE TO ISSUE NOT TO EXCEED $25,000,000 GENERAL OBLIGATION BONDS AND NOTES TO FUND THE PROVIDENCE  HOUSING TRUST FUND TO FINANCE AFFORDABLE  MULTI-FAMILY HOUSING PROJECTS IN THE CITY",
